high_descs: Turn to the left and face the counter between two sinks.
Pick the candle up from the counter.
Turn around and face the toilet.
Put the candle on the back of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Put a candle on the back of the toilet.

high_descs: Move left then left again to face the gold item on the bathroom counter
Pick up the gold item on the bathroom counter next to the sink
Carry the gold item to the right side of the toilet
Place the gold item on the back of the toilet on the far right
anns.task_desc: Move a gold item to the toilet tank

high_descs: turn around to face the double sinks
pick up the bottle of nail polish that is on the counter and closest to the sink on the right
turn back around to face the right side of the toilet
put the bottle of nail polish on the back of the toilet
anns.task_desc: put a bottle of nail polish on the back of the toilet
